<p><span class="bold">Showering Silho...</span></p>
</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="tkkfdp" data-video-descrip="Clark, high on Red Kryptonites, admits he's knowingly stringing Chloe along." data-video-title="Clark Lampshades His Stringing" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/tkkfdp_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/red_clark_on_chloe_moment.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/StringingTheHopelessSuitorAlong" data-video-tropename="Stringing The Hopeless Suitor Along" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Series/Smallville" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/red_clark_on_chloe_moment.jpg">
