<div class="_pmvv-vidbox-desc">
<h1 id="overlay-title">Smallville- Seismic Sex</h1>
<p id="overlay-descrip" class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
When Lana gets superpowers, she and Clark take full advantage. And it's felt all over Smallville.	</p>
<div class="rating-row" data-video-id="h0dujp">
<input type="hidden" name="is_logged_in" value="0">
